 <br>
I would consider it below the Frostbringer for this reason.  DD procs, unless accompanied with a debuff, stun, slow and or dot, rarely generate enough agro by them selves.  There are a few exceptions like Kreizen's Flame (Lure based DD).  The Frostbringer is a 60dd ac debuff... It's enough to generate agro over a lot of other weapons.<br>
